{"data":{"metadata":{"authors":{},"created_at":1637605563000,"identifier":"/docs/globals/hidden","modified_at":1645838554000,"sections":[{"identifier":"hidden","level":1,"text":"Hidden"}],"snippets":[{"identifier":"hidden-preview","script":"<script>\n    import {Box} from \"@kahi-ui/framework\";\n</script>\n\n<Box palette=\"accent\" hidden={[\"mobile\", \"tablet\"]}>\n    I am visible on Desktop / Widescreen Viewports.\n</Box>\n\n<Box\n    palette=\"affirmative\"\n    hidden={[\"desktop\", \"widescreen\"]}\n>\n    I am visible on Mobile / Tablet Viewports.\n</Box>","syntax":"svelte","title":"Hidden Preview"}],"title":"Hidden"},"references":{"custom_properties":{},"events":{},"properties":{"*":[{"name":"hidden","description":"Alters the Component to not render anything or take up physical space in a page's layout.","types":["boolean","{VIEWPORT}"]}]},"slots":{}},"render":"<blockquote data-palette=\"accent\">\n<p><strong>NOTE</strong>: Introduced feature in <code>v0.2.2</code>.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>All Components have access to the <code>data-hidden</code> global HTML attribute via the <code>hidden</code> property. Unlike the standard <a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Global_attributes/hidden\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><code>hidden</code></a> HTML attribute, <code>data-hidden</code> supports <a href=\"../framework/responsitivity\" svelte:prefetch=\"true\">Responsitivity</a>.</p>\n<blockquote data-palette=\"informative\">\n<p><strong>USAGE</strong>: REPL does not support viewport values, resize your Browser to observe this feature.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote data-palette=\"accent\">\n<p><strong>NOTE</strong>: By passing an array, you can set <a href=\"../framework/responsitivity\" svelte:prefetch=\"true\">responsive values</a>. e.g. <code>hidden={[&quot;mobile&quot;, &quot;tablet&quot;]}</code></p>\n</blockquote>\n<pre class=\"highlight language-svelte\" data-identifier=\"hidden-preview\" data-mode=\"repl\" data-syntax=\"svelte\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>script</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token script\"><span class=\"token language-javascript\">\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>Box<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"@kahi-ui/framework\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>script</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>Box</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">palette</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>accent<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">hidden=</span><span class=\"token language-javascript\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token string\">\"mobile\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"tablet\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    I am visible on Desktop / Widescreen Viewports.\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>Box</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>Box</span>\n    <span class=\"token attr-name\">palette</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>affirmative<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token attr-name\">hidden=</span><span class=\"token language-javascript\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token string\">\"desktop\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"widescreen\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    I am visible on Mobile / Tablet Viewports.\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>Box</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre>"}}